To run this project:

Run the code by going to the "run and debug" menu on the left side of the github codespaces tab and clicking "run and debug" while in the "main.py" tab.
Change tab to the tab titled "noVNC."
If you're met with a "connect" button, click it and type "vscode" as the password.
You're all set.

If you ever want to restart the code, you can come back to the codespaces tab and click the green restart button at the top of the screen.

If you ever accidentally close any tabs, you can use the hotkey "ctrl + shift + t" to bring it back.